				  <IMG ID="pic25" SRC="medstar.gif" WIDTH="18" HEIGHT="18" ALT="*"> : A
				  masterpiece / enthralling</P> 
				<P>Ratings are generally averages. A brilliantly acted but poorly
				  directed film may, therefore, be given the same rating, three stars, for
				  example, as would a film that is mediocre in both regards. Specific criticisms
				  will be given in the reviews and will hopefully clarify the reasons a film has
				  been assigned a particular rating or ratings. </P> 
